<comment id="12018" author="712020:8c1c869b-c4be-4401-b6c0-3f69c6178d55" created="Fri, 10 Apr 2026 13:31:45 +0900"><ul> <li>The prompt text asks for a “Dynamic System Instruction” paragraph, but expected JSON only includes <tt>vocal_environment / mission / pacing</tt>. Do we store/render only 3 fields or also the generated paragraph?</li> <li>Requirements say extract from raw script, but prompt input also includes <tt>character_dna</tt>. Should director note be script-only, character-aware, or both?</li> <li>Scope is unclear: is Director Note generated globally for the guide, per POI, per language, or per POI-language?</li> <li>Creator override is required, but not whether override exists only globally or also at per-item level.</li> <li>“Wraps the text before Gemini API” does not define the exact payload contract engineering should send.</li> </ul> </comment>
